    "id": "faqs/general-faqs.md",
    "content": "# FAQ: General Customer Questions\n\n> Sample FAQs. Replace hours, service area, and brands with the shop's real info.\n\n**Q: What are your hours?**\nA: We answer calls and chats 24/7. Standard service hours are Mon–Sat, 7am–7pm; after-hours\n   and emergency dispatch is available [Source: sops/emergency-protocol.md].\n\n**Q: What areas do you serve?**\nA: [SERVICE_AREA — e.g. Greater Miami-Dade & Broward]. If outside the area, we'll refer you.\n\n**Q: Do you service all brands?**\nA: Yes — we repair and maintain all major HVAC brands, and install [BRANDS_CARRIED].\n\n**Q: How fast can someone come out?**\nA: Often same-day for repairs. Exact availability is confirmed from our live calendar.\n\n**Q: Do you offer maintenance plans?**\nA: Yes — our annual plan starts at $189/yr and includes 2 tune-up visits\n   [Source: pricing/ac-repair-2024.md § Maintenance / Tune-Up].\n\n**Q: How long does an AC install take?**\nA: A standard residential swap is usually completed in one day\n   [Source: services/ac-installation.md § Timeline].\n\n**Q: Do you offer financing?**\nA: Yes — 0% for 12 months on qualifying repairs, plus monthly plans on installs\n   [Source: pricing/ac-repair-2024.md § Financing].\n\n**Q: Is the diagnostic fee refundable?**\nA: It's waived if you book the repair on the same visit [Source: pricing/ac-repair-2024.md § Diagnostic Fee].\n"
