    "id": "services/ac-installation.md",
    "content": "# Service: AC Installation / Replacement\n\n> Sample service description. Replace brands, tonnage, and pricing with the shop's real data.\n\n## Overview\nFull residential AC system replacement — condenser, air handler/coil, and thermostat, sized\nto the home with a proper load calculation.\n\n## Timeline\n- **Standard single-system swap:** typically completed in **one day**.\n- **Add-ons** (new ductwork, electrical, permits): may add 1–2 days.\n\n## What's included\n- In-home consult + load sizing (free for installs)\n- Removal & haul-away of the old system\n- New system install + startup test\n- Equipment registration for warranty [Source: sops/warranty-policy.md]\n\n## Pricing approach\n- Installs are quoted after the free consult (varies by tonnage/efficiency/home).\n- Financing: monthly payment plans available [Source: pricing/ac-repair-2024.md § Financing].\n- The AI should **never quote a flat install price** — always book the free consult.\n\n## Good-fit signals for the AI to book a consult\n- \"My unit is 12+ years old / keeps breaking\"\n- \"My energy bills are really high\"\n- \"I've repaired it 2–3 times this year\"\n"
